reviewText: Did you ever think Giselle could be turned into a camp riot? This is not to be missed. Rudi struts and flexes his nether area. Seymour, looking like Giselle's mum, goes all-out mellerdrama, per usual, and chews up the scenery. At one time, this was called "expressive dancing."  Shameless !
Giselle, buscaba interpretado por Julio Bocca, mi madre es una ferviente admiradora de l.
